---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="TROVE - UX/UI | Portfolio ImStryker"
  description="Trove project page"
  lang="en"
>
  <Header lang="en" />
  
  <main class="bg-white">
    
    <!-- HEADER SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-24 text-center">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h1 class="title-main mb-6">
          TROVE
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Role badges -->
        <div class="role-badges">
          <span>My role: UX/UI Designer</span>
          <span class="separator">|</span>
          <span>Web Designer</span>
          <span class="separator">|</span>
          <span>Front End Developer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MOBILE SECTION (Video) -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        <div class="video-container">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dxUyH-GCNa0?autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=dxUyH-GCNa0&controls=0&showinfo=0&rel=0&modestbranding=1"
            title="Trove UX/UI Demo"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            class="video-iframe"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STARTING POINT SECTION -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title mb-12">
          STARTING<br>POINT
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Main descriptive paragraph -->
        <div class="content-grid">
          <div class="main-description">
            <p class="description-main mb-10">
              Trove started as a beta without structure or clear strategy, which affected its conversion, retention and user acquisition
            </p>
            
            <!-- Secondary text -->
            <div class="secondary-text">
              <p>Onboarding was the biggest friction point: long and confusing, with an average time of 9 minutes and no visual guides. Additionally, lack of trust in service security generated 80% abandonment before completion.</p>
              
              <p>The product lacked a clear UX/UI structure, which affected understanding of its purpose: 75% of users had false expectations about its functionality and 7 out of 10 requested cancellation shortly after registering.</p>
              
              <p>It was necessary to rebuild the user experience from scratch, optimizing conversion, improving product perception and structuring the platform to make it more accessible and profitable.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Statistics grid -->
          <div class="stats-grid">
            <!-- Stat 1 -->
            <div class="stat-item">
              <div class="stat-number">9min</div>
              <div class="stat-description">Average time to<br>complete onboarding</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Stat 2 -->
            <div class="stat-item">
              <div class="stat-number">80%</div>
              <div class="stat-description">Abandonment rate in<br>onboarding</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Stat 3 -->
            <div class="stat-item">
              <div class="stat-number-double">
                <span class="main-stat">75%</span>
                <span class="secondary-stat">7/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-description">
                <span>False user expectation</span>
                <span>Early Cancellation Rate</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Custom padding responsive */
  .custom-padding {
    padding-left: 32px;
    padding-right: 32px;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .custom-padding {
      padding-left: 120px;
      padding-right: 120px;
    }
  }

  /* Typography */
  .title-main {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000000;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .role-badges {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #666666;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .separator {
    color: #666666;
    margin: 0 4px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000000;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .description-main {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .secondary-text {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #333333;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .secondary-text p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* Video Container */
  .video-container {
    background-color: #000000;
    border-radius: 40px;
    height: 600px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .video-iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }

  /* Content Grid */
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .main-description {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  /* Stats Grid */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 60px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-number-double {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .main-stat {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .secondary-stat {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-description {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #666666;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .stat-description span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .title-main {
      font-size: 48px;
    }

    .role-badges {
      font-size: 14px;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .separator {
      display: none;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .description-main {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .secondary-text {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .video-container {
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .stat-number,
    .main-stat,
    .secondary-stat {
      font-size: 48px;
    }

    .stat-description {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .title-main {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .description-main {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .video-container {
      height: 300px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .stat-number,
    .main-stat,
    .secondary-stat {
      font-size: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>